      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which shares the same shrouded radial impeller topology as the COU device. Operating conditions overlap with COU range. Blood analog used in validation is an accepted surrogate for whole blood at these shear rates. Validation activities are sufficiently relevant to the COU."
