    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. CFD predictions of NIH agree with experimental measurements within ±18% across all operating points, and the worst-case hemolysis condition is correctly identified. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied for the COU device across all evaluated operating conditions. The package is accepted for regulatory submission in support of the Class II CPB device 510(k).",
